---
// Footer.astro
---

<footer class="bg-primary text-on-primary pt-24 pb-12">
  <div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-gutter">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 mb-20">
      <div class="md:col-span-4 space-y-8">
        <img alt="Fiabilis.ai" class="h-12 w-auto" src="/logo.png" />
        <p class="text-white/60 text-base leading-relaxed max-w-sm font-sans">
          Expertise en paie et conseil social augmentée par l'IA. Pour une conformité sans compromis et une performance RH décuplée.
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <a class="w-11 h-11 rounded-full bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-secondary transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 border border-white/10" href="#" aria-label="LinkedIn">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 fill-current text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19 0h-14c-2.761 0-5 2.239-5 5v14c0 2.761 2.239 5 5 5h14c2.762 0 5-2.239 5-5v-14c0-2.761-2.238-5-5-5zm-11 19h-3v-11h3v11zm-1.5-12.268c-.966 0-1.75-.79-1.75-1.764s.784-1.764 1.75-1.764 1.75.79 1.75 1.764-.783 1.764-1.75 1.764zm13.5 12.268h-3v-5.604c0-3.368-4-3.113-4 0v5.604h-3v-11h3v1.765c1.396-2.586 7-2.777 7 2.476v6.759z"></path></svg>
          </a>
          <a class="w-11 h-11 rounded-full bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-secondary transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 border border-white/10" href="#" aria-label="Twitter">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 fill-current text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M24 4.557c-.883.392-1.832.656-2.828.775 1.017-.609 1.798-1.574 2.165-2.724-.951.564-2.005.974-3.127 1.195-.897-.957-2.178-1.555-3.594-1.555-3.179 0-5.515 2.966-4.797 6.045-4.091-.205-7.719-2.165-10.148-5.144-1.29 2.213-.669 5.108 1.523 6.574-.806-.026-1.566-.247-2.229-.616-.054 2.281 1.581 4.415 3.949 4.89-.693.188-1.452.232-2.224.084.626 1.956 2.444 3.379 4.6 3.419-2.07 1.623-4.678 2.348-7.29 2.04 2.179 1.397 4.768 2.212 7.548 2.212 9.142 0 14.307-7.721 13.995-14.646.962-.695 1.797-1.562 2.457-2.549z"></path></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="md:col-span-2 space-y-6">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-lg tracking-tight text-white font-display">Solutions</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm text-white/50">
          <li><a class="hover:text-secondary transition-colors" href="#">Expertis IA</a></li>
          <li><a class="hover:text-secondary transition-colors" href="#">Audit Social</a></li>
          <li><a class="hover:text-secondary transition-colors" href="#">Conventions Collectives</a></li>
          <li><a class="hover:text-secondary transition-colors" href="#">Droit URSSAF</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="md:col-span-2 space-y-6">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-lg tracking-tight text-white font-display">Société</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm text-white/50">
          <li><a class="hover:text-secondary transition-colors" href="#">À propos</a></li>
          <li><a class="hover:text-secondary transition-colors" href="#">Expertise</a></li>
          <li><a class="hover:text-secondary transition-colors" href="#">Carrières</a></li>
          <li><a class="hover:text-secondary transition-colors" href="#">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="md:col-span-4 space-y-6">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-lg tracking-tight text-white font-display">Contact</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-5 text-sm text-white/50">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl text-white">location_on</span>
            </div>
            Paris, France
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl text-white">mail</span>
            </div>
            contact@fiabilis.ai
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl text-white">phone</span>
            </div>
            +33 (0)1 00 00 00 00
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="pt-10 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-6 text-[13px] text-white/30">
      <p>© {new Date().getFullYear()} Fiabilis.ai - Conseil en paie augmenté par l'IA. Tous droits réservés.</p>
      <div class="flex gap-10">
        <a class="hover:text-white transition-colors" href="#">Mentions légales</a>
        <a class="hover:text-white transition-colors" href="#">Confidentialité</a>
        <a class="hover:text-white transition-colors" href="#">CGU</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
